Why don't we put them on?
我们何不穿上？

257
00:17:00,850 --> 00:17:03,820
Get a picture of Batman and James Bond, together.
拍一张蝙蝠侠和 詹姆士庞德一起的照片

258
00:17:04,020 --> 00:17:06,450
